eaee","tid":462154,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學到野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次比條撚樣督我出黎 今次我仲唔玩撚死你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 努力啊師弟"},{"pid":"954a60a5c3a3378bd8bb15aaa17055dfc220bd03","tid":462154,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前我朋友都遇都樓豬呢種人<br />\n佢直接揾professor屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後條友之後臭名遠播，final year pj自己一個一組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港Professor幾好 外國果D真係唔理你"},{"pid":"1471086c2d11ed95568bd09101052404c0606546","tid":462154,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"我最成日聽係deadline個陣電腦壞左😂"},{"pid":"fdebbbad2c3cef269660f00bdbfdf3c003b7f115","tid":462154,"uid":94929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:01:38.000Z","msg":"識過一個咁既人<br />\n平時一堆偉論 係prof面前問好多野 又會話大家最好早啲做好<br />\n結果deadline前個日就會消失/交垃圾文不對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6752b363e75f32f67ad1becbfce6a83d2ba632","tid":462154,"uid":17823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"就係你啲啲仆街 做左啲垃圾copy and paste 搞到成組即係我要執埋條友個份 條友交個陣仲要擺出自己做得好好嘅樣出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f00ff6d160d2b6b0b0876e9f74f175a26c71f0","tid":462154,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 肯做野既groupmate(s)多數都會搵professor consult project，呢個時侯無論你幾想free ride都一定要出現，等professor覺得你都有做過，去到唔洗出聲，等組員問野就得；<br />\n<br />\n2. 平時肯做野既組員喺group提出意見時，你一定要應機，求其答吓「that's too advanced.」，「岩呀，有data analysis會有說服力好多！」，「同意」，「我好想幫多D」，「我地都好想幫手」，「我會做research」，「我搵過d data」咁樣被人report時都可以show到證據，話自己有參與討論；<br />\n<br />\n3. 當要交project outline或者final report時，就緊係深潛。首先你要講明自己有幫手既心，之後一直唔喺WhatsApp上水，去到deadline前果日點好？緊係問吓會做野既組員做成點，check吓佢進度，叫佢send份野出黎。你見到組員已經做好份野，一定要應佢「我已經做左好多research，資料都睇左好多了！」；<br />\n<br />\n4. 組員分配task(s)俾自己後，你乜都唔洗做，就算做都係交份垃圾俾佢就ok！如果組員話你英文好廢，內容有問題，copy and paste都可以做錯，你要答佢「當然啦，我知你英文最勁，我無你咁叻呀，但我都好想幫手架！」；<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果你係Final year既，咁就仲簡單，你唔應機就可以話自己「sor呀我岩岩聽緊個好重要既recruitment talk」，「sor呀你都知Final year好忙」，「sor呀我岩岩返緊工，好忙」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有漏，其他專業Free rider可以補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係個句大排檔都要請返餐（全組）<br />\n有錢出錢有力出力，講咩都冇用"},{"pid":"211fb253df1d5e1590989603d33ce56b7df8f941","tid":462154,"uid":93855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"thanks樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5359b9b05c3396ff69e23d5c3b7a987d623861d6","tid":462154,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c41a339c68476c897962bbf4d71eaa57bd54224","tid":462154,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80a424387b31265fafd1cc2165d970f6decbec46","tid":462154,"uid":111293,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 肯做野既groupmate(s)多數都會搵professor consult project，呢個時侯無論你幾想free ride都一定要出現，等professor覺得你都有做過，去到唔洗出聲，等組員問野就得；<br />\n<br />\n2. 平時肯做野既組員喺group提出意見時，你一定要應機，求其答吓「that's too advanced.」，「岩呀，有data analysis會有說服力好多！」，「同意」，「我好想幫多D」，「我地都好想幫手」，「我會做research」，「我搵過d data」咁樣被人report時都可以show到證據，話自己有參與討論；<br />\n<br />\n3. 當要交project outline或者final report時，就緊係深潛。首先你要講明自己有幫手既心，之後一直唔喺WhatsApp上水，去到deadline前果日點好？緊係問吓會做野既組員做成點，check吓佢進度，叫佢send份野出黎。你見到組員已經做好份野，一定要應佢「我已經做左好多research，資料都睇左好多了！」；<br />\n<br />\n4. 組員分配task(s)俾自己後，你乜都唔洗做，就算做都係交份垃圾俾佢就ok！如果組員話你英文好廢，內容有問題，copy and paste都可以做錯，你要答佢「當然啦，我知你英文最勁，我無你咁叻呀，但我都好想幫手架！」；<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果你係Final year既，咁就仲簡單，你唔應機就可以話自己「sor呀我岩岩聽緊個好重要既recruitment talk」，「sor呀你都知Final year好忙」，「sor呀我岩岩返緊工，好忙」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有漏，其他專業Free rider可以補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開學第一個星期係最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識到班朋友一個sem請食一次飯就得<br />\n<br />\n利申：free ride咗兩年，所有project都有B或以上"},{"pid":"49e0c6faddb3ce00e05434b5d07192a851ae2bcf","tid":462154,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:20:34.000Z","msg":"最撚憎free rider<br />\n你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3343582a5f2fa60ad7d26fc9826c58aa844de1ff","tid":462154,"uid":47255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:23:15.000Z","msg":"睇完之後 學識細分資深freerider"},{"pid":"3185e02edab296acc5c0d6b7e9849056f3e05fc1","tid":462154,"uid":90657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"我相信樓主係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074654f6555737f9cbaeb931272310638680dcc8","tid":462154,"uid":44690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"從來唔同呢嗰人一group，因為物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe4b4f376a1f7ec53278b55e0216f827bfdeb3f","tid":462154,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"1.女<br />\n2.生得靚"},{"pid":"e36299a92c6d6058a918954fed60d1a09ba109ca","tid":462154,"uid":66195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"親身經驗<br />\n<br />\n一定要周圍屌組員做得廢 仲之見人就屌組員，<br />\n<br />\n例如人地做左份野就周圍問老師，同學有咩可以改，再借機屌下組員垃圾，之後就張同學意見重複一次比組員聽，之後叫組員重做"},{"pid":"f4e7a0ff5741cb6f657f8471dfec043b696fb78b","tid":462154,"uid":78988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"祝天下所有freerider俾人屌屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cb7ef5a6291ab4676b1cb50a23fe9f78c23076","tid":462154,"uid":19778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 冇做就係冇做 扮咩鬼野姐你<br />\n做衰野仲要扮埋野就最黑人憎<br />\n到時比人玩 比人唱 就唔好怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485e5f6888ccd019e54e0cd035d81c31686626fb","tid":462154,"uid":19778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"之前同個freerider一姐 同樓主形容嗰種差唔多<br />\n<br />\n比我堂堂屌 見到面就當面見  係朋友面前就大聲屌專登俾佢聽到  係whatsapp group得閒又屌下佢<br />\n<br />\n雖然要做埋佢嗰份野 但當發洩下都幾好 侮辱到佢之餘又可以減壓  仲可以令到佢冇晒朋友神憎鬼厭<br />\n你都咪話唔爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967d97c225110135ac1ed1fb936562b7d694378e","tid":462154,"uid":19778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前同個freerider一姐 同樓主形容嗰種差唔多<br />\n<br />\n比我堂堂屌 見到面就當面見  係朋友面前就大聲屌專登俾佢聽到  係whatsapp group得閒又屌下佢<br />\n<br />\n雖然要做埋佢嗰份野 但當發洩下都幾好 侮辱到佢之餘又可以減壓  仲可以令到佢冇晒朋友神憎鬼厭<br />\n你都咪話唔爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最開心係 當大家都好憎一個人既時間 咁大家就可以一齊針鳩佢 慢慢做埋朋友  勁爽  <br />\n真係多謝個freerider 比機會我識到咁多fd 開開心心咁返學"},{"pid":"ad0f97376656db665d851f812d210b57718564dc","tid":462154,"uid":141918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母freerider食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb3445e86dfffcfdac5a9903d79240f07aee310","tid":462154,"uid":36329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n不過讀書個陣有條友咁樣做最後我地都冇寫佢個名落份功課到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ef821621d933eca2401e614be3f890f02b0b25","tid":462154,"uid":99893,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"其實冇用 一去對質已經知咩料<br />\n<br />\n利申 4年都踢爆過10幾個freerider 搞到佢哋F哂 要retake"},{"pid":"f91a27c5db70a00751d3bb89c624ab027c49d567","tid":462154,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"下次使唔使做賊做強姦殺人犯上來開po教人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33df1ad98de3dfd2f6e24a44af603811a8e705a0","tid":462154,"uid":77663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:00:10.000Z","msg":"我試過一個人撐起全組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知我一申請調走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成組一齊炒車 露出佢哋嘅freerider真本性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得一個比較肯做野之外，其他就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919eb185b429d6adf6e1d0cb047b236070b0afc9","tid":462154,"uid":62085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:07:40.000Z","msg":"引晒啲freerider出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fea4d3a398d0e7cc7ce461e036c501efdd2c0c","tid":462154,"uid":74824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:16:02.000Z","msg":"最柒憎freerider<img src=\"/asset